    "description": {
      "value": "<p>An eidolon's body becomes resistant to harm, granting it damage reduction.</p>\n<p>Choose one alignment: chaotic, evil, good, or lawful. The eidolon gains DR 5 that can be bypassed by weapons that possess the chosen alignment.</p>\n<p>The alignment must be opposite to one of the alignments possessed by the eidolon. At 12th level, this protection can be increased to DR 10 by spending 2 additional evolution points.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>The summoner must be at least 9th level before selecting this evolution.</p>\n<p><strong>Usage</strong></p>\n<p>Add DR to eidolon character sheet.</p>",
